 cache implementation:
 LRU cache
    cache has tag indicating when a line was last used
    when need to store something in line
        replace item with the LRU tag -> oldest tag

    whenever item inserted into cache line update tag of updated
       this is the PC
    whenever item has cache line hit, reset flag
 
 
 


 have cache store when it first loads -> initial PC
 assign tag when item placed in cache
    before placing things in cache, see if line valid and if tag matches
 have flag or condition when cache full
 determine whether hit occurs
 have updated value set when line is hit 
 do search for oldest item when cache is full, no hits
     when item retrieved from memory, place it in cache


 valid tag, last updated, tag, data
 
